<P> 
<Q REND="inline">'And what thanks you gave me for it!' &s;aid
Standfa&s;t. Don't you remember the little auburn haired wench at
Ghent?'</Q></P>
<P> 
<Q REND="inline">'What the coun&s;ellor's wi&s;e?' cried the
