friend. Ah major you never got the &s;tart of <PB N="69" REF="102"> me but in
this la&s;t bu&s;ine&s;s. How different things u&s;ed to be. The gaye&s;t, the
mo&s;t accompli&s;hed yielded to me in the art of plea&s;ing, and till I was
&s;atisfied none dared attempt to make a choice.&mdash;Now, a fooli&s;h woman,
