adventures at Little Hockley was prudence to this.'</Q></P>
<P>He had &s;carcely &s;poken when Lady Hazard came abruptly into
the room. Addre&s;&s;ing her&s;elf to her hu&s;band, &s;he &s;aid, 
<Q REND="inline">'My lord, I know not how you will receive the
